text: On a Magical Night () is a 2019 French Belgian Luxembourgian comedy movie directed by Christophe Honoré and starring Chiara Mastroianni, Vincent Lacoste, Benjamin Biolay, Camille Cottin, Carole Bouquet, Marie-Christine Adam. ==Other websites== * * Category:2019 comedy movies Category:French comedy movies Category:Belgian comedy movies Category:Luxembourgian comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Christophe Honoré
title: On a Magical Night
